================
=1. QUICK START=
================

==================
1.1. Requirements
==================
  - Python >= 2.6 with package python-dev
  - python-setuptools 
  - openmpi (http://www.open-mpi.org/) with package openmpi-dev or libopenmpi-dev
  -	R >= 2.14.0+ (http://www.r-project.org/) with packages pROC (http://web.expasy.org/pROC/) and Cairo (http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/Cairo/index.html)
   
==================
1.2. Installation
==================
To install iRNA, the setuptools mechanism can be used: 
	
	./python setup.py build
	./python setup.py install
	
iRNA will download automatically the package = numpy, scipy, mpi4py, rpy2, sqlitebck, lxml and suds.
In case of problem, use : 
easy_install numpy scipy mpi4py rpy2 sqlitebck lxml suds
and retry previous command. 

